Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威路斯基博士，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美防卫罩突然暴增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔族的反应也急速增大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.51,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能，速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防卫罩里面的温度上升中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以引起周围温度跟着变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.66,0:02:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8区的系统降低至3级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.76,0:02:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法修复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等3，5，6空失效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源回路故障...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第14区，必须封锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E一7回路，因为系统倒数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.50,0:02:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.27,0:02:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第6区的系统降低至4级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第17区的系统降低至3级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.04,0:02:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第1，3，4，5的辅助炉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修复需要多少时间?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少需要3个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那么多时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.05,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到1个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的完成体就会完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是以我们的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在短期间内修复，实在是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道没有其他办法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我试着让那防护罩降低再生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.47,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那期间请加速修复工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防护罩停止扩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，快去进行修复工作   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你说我有我可以做到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...怎么会这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.95,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力炉找到有4个地方无法条复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去，补充能源系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,60%已经是极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!这样根本得到预定的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你试过利用2等回路了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，2等回路已经使用于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样，就直接接上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不行，7个回路之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经有4个直接连接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去炉心无法支撑下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底...到底要怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想对刚才的问题做点意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请使用我们的能源吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们钢铁天使拥有系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以将自己的能源转换其他能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后利用这点，来增加主机力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以，这样做的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的机能就会停止，然后死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确如果在动力炉里面增加能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.59,0:05:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许可以使质量增加百分百以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护人类是钢天使的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们的命可以达成目的的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话，我们会更加感到荣耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人的想法也和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了       威路斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.35,0:06:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会勉强你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.01,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始做最后的作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源转换系统准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，将动力炉的系统启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.42,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将动力移转倒转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将质量由0转至4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防护罩又开始扩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.66,0:07:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...别再展开恶魔的翅膀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生，好点了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还很痛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.12,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.18,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都做不到...我什么都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么拥有拯救久留美的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本完全没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.66,0:09:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我...我并不合适久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲什么...傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌这样的仲人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我并不愿意讲出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是一心一意对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美姊姊的仲人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你为了久留美姊姊而哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.59,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生，请提起精神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜应该是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要从此分别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第5区，修复率85%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第9，12区，修复率65%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B一2回路，B一3回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部完成直接接续V回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第11区，修复率52%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第18区，修复率64%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8区，修复率55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防护罩的速度加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.50,0:10:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.97,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人  你怎么可以起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...      他在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在制止久留美的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.06,0:11:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的力量可以拯救久留美吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城博士   绫小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜，仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美必须被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有其他办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以...不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.74,0:12:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐，我...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“罪与罚”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回   最终话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.21,0:14:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回   最终话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请保特房间光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与电视保持距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别错过最后结局唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜，仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.16,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美必须被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力炉已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始进行倒数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人   我好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
